metadata.name: Night Sky #1
metadata.description:
Night Sky #1 is my first release on the Foundation.

It shows a wild camp illuminated, under the Milky Way, on the edge of the Boa Vista Canyon, in Sao Jose dos Ausentes, Brazil.

This photograph was accepted at the XIX Biennial of Brazilian Photographic Art in Colors, when it participated in several exhibitions.

Title: Boa Vista Canyon Camp
Photographer: Eduardo Bassotto
Edition: 1/1
Dimensions: 6016 x 4016px
